Maori bug
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Platyzosteria novae seelandiae</i>, black beetle, a native stink-roach, also called black beetle


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
